## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of Maslow's influence on teaching practices. Additionally, the application of Maslow's theory can vary significantly depending on the educational context and individual educator's interpretation. Further research and practical application in diverse educational settings would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the theory's impact.